On the brink of a midlife crisis, 30-something 
Mike O'Donnell (Matthew Perry) wishes he could have 
a "do-over." And that's exactly what he gets when 
he wakes up one morning to find he's 17 years old 
again. With his adult mind stuck inside the body 
of a teenager (Zac Efron), Mike actually has the 
chance to reverse some decisions he wishes he'd 
never made. But maybe they weren't so bad after 
all. Leslie Mann and Michelle Trachtenberg co-star.

Starring: Matthew Perry, Zac Efron
